      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/2/5",
      "text": [
        " اَلرِّضَا عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : « لَيْلَةُ خَمْسَةٍ وَ عِشْرِينَ مِنْ ذِي اَلْقَعْدَةِ دُحِيَتِ اَلْأَرْضُ مِنْ تَحْتِ اَلْكَعْبَةِ فَمَنْ صَامَ ذَلِكَ اَلْيَوْمَ كَانَ كَمَنْ صَامَ سِتِّينَ شَهْراً »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2300 - Imam Ali ibn Musa Ar-Ridha (as) said:\n\"On the night of the 25th of Dhu al-Qa'dah, the earth was spread out from beneath the Kaaba. Whoever fasts on that day, it is as if they have fasted for sixty months.\""
        ]
      }
    },
